<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>목차 - 홀로서기 심리학</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <nav class="nav">
                <a href="/" class="logo">홀로서기 심리학</a>
                <ul class="nav-list">
                    <li><a href="/">홈</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/chapters">목차</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">책 소개</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="main">
        <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title">목차</h1>
        <p class="page-description">홀로서기 심리학의 10개 챕터를 통해 심리적 독립을 향한 여정을 시작하세요.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<section class="chapters-list">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="chapters-container">
            <% book.chapters.forEach((chapter, index) => { %>
            <div class="chapter-item">
                <div class="chapter-info">
                    <div class="chapter-header">
                        <span class="chapter-number">Chapter <%= chapter.id %></span>
                        <h2 class="chapter-title">
                            <a href="/chapter/<%= chapter.id %>"><%= chapter.title %></a>
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="chapter-subtitle"><%= chapter.subtitle %></h3>
                    <p class="chapter-summary"><%= chapter.summary %></p>

                    <div class="chapter-details">
                        <div class="key-points">
                            <h4>주요 내용</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <% chapter.keyPoints.forEach(point => { %>
                                <li><%= point %></li>
                                <% }); %>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="chapter-benefit">
                            <h4>기대 효과</h4>
                            <p><%= chapter.benefits %></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="chapter-actions">
                    <a href="/chapter/<%= chapter.id %>" class="btn btn-primary">자세히 보기</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% if (index < book.chapters.length - 1) { %>
            <div class="chapter-divider"></div>
            <% } %>
            <% }); %>
        </div>

        <div class="chapters-navigation">
            <div class="nav-item">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-item">
                <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary">책 소개 보기</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="reading-guide">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="guide-card">
            <h3>💡 독서 가이드</h3>
            <div class="guide-content">
                <div class="guide-item">
                    <h4>순차적 읽기</h4>
                    <p>1장부터 10장까지 순서대로 읽으면서 체계적으로 심리적 독립을 학습하세요.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="guide-item">
                    <h4>관심 주제 우선</h4>
                    <p>특별히 관심 있는 주제의 챕터를 먼저 읽고, 연관된 다른 챕터로 확장하세요.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="guide-item">
                    <h4>실습과 함께</h4>
                    <p>각 챕터의 실습 내용을 일상에 적용하며 천천히 변화를 경험하세요.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>홀로서기 심리학</h3>
                    <p>진정한 나를 찾아가는 심리적 독립의 여정</p>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>목차</h4>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="/chapters">전체 목차</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/chapter/1">1장. 의존의 뿌리를 파헤치다</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/chapter/5">5장. 스스로 결정하는 용기</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/chapter/10">10장. 성숙한 관계로의 여정</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h4>연락처</h4>
                    <p>이메일: jihajoung5001@gmail.com</p>
                    <p>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/jiha-j">jiha-j</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2024 홀로서기 심리학. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>